'''波士頓市政廳'''（{{lang-en|Boston City Hall}}）是[[美國|美國]][[波士頓|波士頓]]市政府所在地，{{link-en|波士頓市長|Mayor of Boston}}的辦公室與{{link-en|波士頓市議會|Boston City Council}}皆位於此。現在的市政廳修建於1968年<ref name=nytimes>{{cite news|first=Dennis|last=Hevesi|title=Gerhard Kallmann, Architect, Is Dead at 97|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/25/arts/design/gerhard-kallmann-architect-dies-at-97.html?_r=1|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|publisher=|date=2012-06-24|accessdate=2012-07-16|archive-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213100010/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/25/arts/design/gerhard-kallmann-architect-dies-at-97.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

波士頓市政廳是一座典型的[[粗野主义|粗野主义]]建築<ref name=throwback2014>{{citation |title=Throwback Thursday: When Boston’s City Hall Was New (and Already Unloved) |date=February 13, 2014 |work=Boston Magazine |url=http://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/blog/2014/02/13/throwback-thursday-bostons-city-hall-new-already-unloved/ |accessdate=February 13, 2014 |archive-date=2016-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601120153/http://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/blog/2014/02/13/throwback-thursday-bostons-city-hall-new-already-unloved/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，外觀極具爭議。波士頓市政廳被《建築周刊》網站評為最偉大建築之一<ref>{{cite web | title = Boston City Hall listing on Great Buildings Online | url = http://www.greatbuildings.com/buildings/Boston_City_Hall.html | accessdate = 2006-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201213004734/http://www.greatbuildings.com/buildings/Boston_City_Hall.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，卻也在網路評選中被評為世界最醜陋建築<ref>[http://www.boston.com/news/local/breaking_news/2008/11/boston_city_hal_1.html Boston City Hall tops ugliest-building list] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/news/local/breaking_news/2008/11/boston_city_hal_1.html |date=20140227210111 }}. ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]''</ref><ref>reuters.com [http://www.reuters.com/article/lifestyleMolt/idUSTRE4AD2V720081114?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0 Travel Picks: 10 top ugly buildings and monuments] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/lifestyleMolt/idUSTRE4AD2V720081114?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0 |date=20210117194618 }}</ref>。2013年，《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》將市政廳評為波士頓最醜陋建築，並建議拆除<ref>''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]'' [http://www.bostonglobe.com/opinion/2013/09/23/boston-city-hall-should-torn-down/ City Hall Should Torn Down] 2013/09/23</ref>。《加利福尼亞家庭與設計》將波士頓市政廳評為「25座現在就該拆除的建築」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.californiahomedesign.com/inspiration/25-buildings-demolish-right-now/slide/5074 |title=25 Buildings to Demolish Right Now |work=California Home + Design|access-date=2015-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115113131/http://www.californiahomedesign.com/inspiration/25-buildings-demolish-right-now/slide/5074 |archive-date=2018-11-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。波士頓市政府也有重新開發市政廳一帶土地的想法<ref>Casey Ross. [http://www.boston.com/business/articles/2011/03/16/after_many_false_starts_a_new_city_hall_plaza_plan/ A 10-year plan for City Hall Plaza: New incremental approach starts with remodeled T station, trees] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/business/articles/2011/03/16/after_many_false_starts_a_new_city_hall_plaza_plan/ |date=20160303210255 }}. Boston Globe, March 16, 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.boston.com/business/gallery/boston_city_hall_plaza_ideas/ What do you think should be done to City Hall Plaza?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/business/gallery/boston_city_hall_plaza_ideas/ |date=20160304072853 }} Boston Globe, March 16, 2011</ref>。

